	"contentText": "Course Info\n  \n  \n  \n    \n\n\nESBM 3700: Entrepreneurial Environments\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDate and Time\n8/21/2025 - 12/5/2025: TuTh: 12:30pm - 1:45pm\n\n\nInstructor\nSina Sokhan (sina@colorado.edu)\n\n\nClass Location\nKOBL 140\n\n\nTeaching Assistant\nSarvenaz Hashemiborzabadi (sarvenaz.hashemiborzabadi@colorado.edu)\n\n\nOffice Hours\n\nTuesday, 11am-12:30pmPlease signup here\n    \n\nLinks to an external site. anduse this link\n    \n\nLinks to an external site. for zoom meeting.\n\n\n\nSyllabus\nSyllabus\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\n\n\nFinal Presentation Guidelines\nFinal Presentation Guidelines\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\n\n\nStudy Guide\nStudy Guide\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nCourse Calendar\n\n\n\n\n\n\nSession\nDate\nTopic\nInfo\n\n\n\n\n\n\n1\n8/21 (Thursday)\n\nIntroduction\n\n\n \n\n\n\n2\n8/26 (Tuesday)\n\nEntrepreneurial Mindset\n\n\n\n\n3\n8/28 (Thursday)\n\nFrom Ideas to Opportunities\n\n\n\"Entrepreneurial Mindset\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n\n4\n9/2 (Tuesday)\n\nBusiness Models\n\n\n\"Ideas to Opportunities\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n\n5\n9/4 (Thursday)\n\nSources of Funding \n\n\n\"Business Models\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n\n6\n9/9 (Tuesday)\n\nLean Startup \n\n\"Sources of Funding\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n7\n9/11 (Thursday)\n\nLean Startup Exercise\n\n\n\"Lean Startup\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n\n8\n9/16 (Tuesday)\nEntrepreneur Guest\n\"The Founder\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n9\n9/18 (Thursday)\n\nVenture Pitching \n\n\n \n\n\n\n10\n9/23 (Tuesday)\n\nChoosing Your Customer \n\n\n\"Venture Pitching\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n\n11\n9/25 (Thursday)\nChoosing Your Technology\n\"Customer\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n12\n9/30 (Tuesday)\nTeam Work\n\"Technology\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n13\n10/2 (Thursday)\n\nChoosing Your Identity   \n\n\n\n\n14\n10/7 (Tuesday)\n\nChoosing Your Competition\n\n\n\"Identity\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n\n15\n10/9 (Thursday)\nMidsemester Reading Day\n\n\n\n16\n10/14 (Tuesday)\nQuiz\nQuiz will begin at 12:30 pm. You can take it at home, using Proctorio\n\n\n17\n10/16 (Thursday)\nDisruption Strategy\n\"Competition\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n18\n10/21 (Tuesday)\nEntrepreneur Guest\n\"Disruption\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n19\n10/23 (Thursday)\nIntellectual Property Strategy \n \n\n\n20\n10/28 (Tuesday)\nValue Chain Strategy \n \"Intellectual Property\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n21\n10/30 (Thursday)\nEntrepreneur Guest\n \"Value Chain\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n22\n11/4 (Tuesday)\nArchitectural Strategy \n\n\n\n23\n11/6 (Thursday)\nTeam Work\n \"Architectural\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n24\n11/11 (Tuesday)\nStartup Failure \n\n\n\n25\n11/13 (Thursday)\nEntrepreneur Guest\n\"Startup Failure\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n26\n11/18 (Tuesday)\nShark Tank\n\"Flash of Genius\" assignment due at 12:30 pm\n\n\n27\n11/20 (Thursday)\nPresentation\n\n\n\n28\n11/25 (Tuesday)\nThanksgiving \nEnjoy the holidays!\n\n\n29\n11/27 (Thursday)\nThanksgiving \nEnjoy the holidays! \n\n\n30\n12/2 (Tuesday)\nPresentation\n \n\n\n31\n12/4 (Thursday)\nPresentation\n \n\n\n33\n12/9 (Tuesday)\nFinal Exam\nFinal exam begins at 4:30 pm.You can take it at home, using Proctorio.\n\n\n\n \n                    \n \n \n  \n  \n\n",
